azy!
Anyway, after the deal, regulators=C2=A0of course=C2=A0checked into whether=
 anyone who worked on the deal, or their contacts, traded in the stock. Lou=
don=E2=80=99s wife mentioned this to him, and he realized what he had done:
One week later, on April 3, 2023, Loudon confessed to his wife that he had =
traded in TA prior to the acquisition announcement. Loudon did not tell her=
