=E2=80=9CI was doing it for you!=E2=80=9D Bad!
Stunned by this revelation, Loudon=E2=80=99s wife reported the trading to h=
er supervisor at BP. In turn, BP placed her on administrative leave. BP rev=
iewed Loudon=E2=80=99s wife=E2=80=99s emails and texts, finding no evidence=
