Well, so, she=E2=80=99s not working long hours anymore.
After Loudon=E2=80=99s confession, Loudon=E2=80=99s wife moved out of their=
 house and generally ceased all contact with Loudon. A few weeks later, Lou=
don delivered a handwritten note to his wife apologizing for violating her =
