  [6] Also, if you do the crude thing I suggest =E2=80=94 buy PSH, crack it=
 open, sell the stocks =E2=80=94 you have a lot of market risk during the t=
rade, and selling the stocks all at once might drag their prices down. In p=
ractice the better way to do this is what Elliott apparently did: You buy P=
