xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Elon Mus=
k</a>.) But the banks were burned by the outrageously good deals they gave =
out in 2022, so they could only offer pretty bad deals in 2023. Now they ar=
